      • Exam

        public Exam(java.lang.String filename,
            java.time.LocalDate date,
            java.time.LocalDate unpublishDate,
            boolean unpublished,
            int courseId)
        Creates an Exam object.
        Parameters:
        filename - The filename of the Exam. Must be at least two characters long and cannot be null.
        date - The date of the Exam. Cannot be null.
        unpublishDate - The date at which the Exam should be unpublished from the website. Cannot be null.
        unpublished - Set to true if this Exam should NOT be published on the website, otherwise false.
        courseId - The ID of the Course to which an Exam belongs. Cannot be null.
